Template: campsite/url
Type: string
Default: campsite
Description: Campsite Site URL
 You must define the Campsite site URL
 Your Campsite site would be accessed http://localhost/<siteurl>
 By default : http://localhost/campsite
 .
 If you want to configure it later, you should run 'dpkg-reconfigure campsite'.

Template: campsite/dbname
Type: string
Default: campsite
Description: Campsite database Name
 You must define Campsite database
 .
 If you want to configure it later, you should run 'dpkg-reconfigure campsite'.

Template: campsite/dbusername
Type: string
Default: campsiteuser
Description: Campsite database User
 You must define Campsite database user
 .
 If you want to configure it later, you should run 'dpkg-reconfigure campsite'.

Template: campsite/db_admname
Type: string
Default: root
Description: Campsite database Administrator
 You must define Campsite database administrator
 .
 If you want to configure it later, you should run 'dpkg-reconfigure campsite'.

Template: campsite/db_userpassword
Type: string
Default: campsitedbuser
Description: Campsite database User Password
 You must define Campsite database user password
 .
 If you want to configure it later, you should run 'dpkg-reconfigure campsite'.

Template: campsite/db_admpassword
Type: string
Default: campsite
Description: Campsite database Administrator Password
 You must define Campsite database administrator password
 .
 If you want to configure it later, you should run 'dpkg-reconfigure campsite'.

Template: campsite/dbserver
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: Campsite database Server
 You must define Campsite database Server
 .
 If you want to configure it later, you should run 'dpkg-reconfigure campsite'.

Template: campsite/dbsample
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Campsite template demo
 Do you want to install database for template demo ?
 .
 If you want to configure it later, you should run 'dpkg-reconfigure campsite'.

Template: campsite/email
Type: string
Default: youraccount@yourdomain.org
Description: Campsite Email Address
 Enter your e-mail address, this will be the e-mail address of the site  Administrator.
 .
 If you want to configure it later, you should run 'dpkg-reconfigure campsite'.

Template: campsite/sitename
Type: string
Default: My Campsite Site
Description: Campsite Site Name
 Enter the name of your Campsite site name.
 .
 If you want to configure it later, you should run 'dpkg-reconfigure campsite'.

Template: campsite/webserver
Type: multiselect
Choices: apache, apache-ssl, apache-perl, apache2
Default: apache2
Description: Web server(s) that should be configured automatically:
 Choose your webserver
 .
 If you want to configure it later, you should run 'dpkg-reconfigure campsite'.

Template: campsite/dbremove
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Remove Database
 Do you want to remove database ?
